(2)\;\;\;a\neq 0\Longrightarrow \operatorname{Res}_{z=\pm ai}(f)=\lim_{z\to\pm ai}(z\mp ai)\,f(z)=\lim_{z\to \pm ai}\frac{ze^{iz}}{z\mp ai}=\frac{\pm aie^{\mp a}}{\pm 2ai}=\frac{e^{\mp a}}{2}
